Feature: get-features error management

    @xray
    Scenario: Error 400 when retrieving feature files from xray

        Given 'XC_DEFAULT_TEST_PLAN' environment variable has been set to 'UNKNOWN_TEST_PLAN'
        When  Xray Connector retrieves feature files from Xray
        Then  An execution error should be reported
        And   The error message should contain 'Error 400'

    @xray
    Scenario: Error 401 when retrieving feature files from xray

        Given The reference test plan is 'RDCHAPQA-48'
        And   'JIRA_XRAY_LOGIN' environment variable has been set to 'UNKNOWN_LOGIN'
        When  Xray Connector retrieves feature files from Xray
        Then  An execution error should be reported
        And   The error message should contain 'Error 401'

