    @xray
    Scenario: Unknown error when retrieving feature files from xray

        Given The reference test plan is 'RDCHAPQA-48'
        And   'JIRA_XRAY_HOST' environment variable has been set to 'jira.dt.renault.com\n'
        When  Xray Connector retrieves feature files from Xray
        Then  An execution error should be reported
        And   The error message should contain 'Unknown error'

